    <title>基于React脚手架集成Cesium</title>
    <link href="https://lyliiyong.github.io/posts/4a17b156.html"/>
    <id>https://lyliiyong.github.io/posts/4a17b156.html</id>
    <published>2023-04-02T06:22:42.432Z</published>
    <updated>2023-04-02T13:31:46.789Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="tip home"><h1 id="创建一个React项目"><a href="#创建一个React项目" class="headerlink" title="创建一个React项目"></a>创建一个React项目</h1></div><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create-react-app cesium-app --template typescript</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tip home"><h1 id="安装模块"><a href="#安装模块" class="headerlink" title="安装模块"></a>安装模块</h1></div><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yarn add @craco/craco@alpha craco-cesium cesium resium</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tip home"><h1 id="重写package-json"><a href="#重写package-json" class="headerlink" title="重写package.json"></a>重写<code>package.json</code></h1></div><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;scripts&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attr">&quot;start&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;craco start&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attr">&quot;build&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;craco build&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attr">&quot;test&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;craco test&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attr">&quot;eject&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;react-scripts eject&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tip home"><h1 id="创建-craco-配置文件"><a href="#创建-craco-配置文件" class="headerlink" title="创建 craco 配置文件"></a>创建 craco 配置文件</h1></div><p>在项目根目录中创建：<code>craco.config.js</code><br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">module</span>.<span class="property">exports</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">plugins</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">plugin</span>: <span class="built_in">require</span>(<span class="string">&quot;craco-cesium&quot;</span>)()</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><div class="tip home"><h1 id="完成"><a href="#完成" class="headerlink" title="完成"></a>完成</h1></div><br>按如下方式导入cesium<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; <span class="title class_">Viewer</span>, <span class="title class_">Entity</span>, <span class="title class_">Color</span> &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;cesium&quot;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>如果使用的是Resium，则可以按如下方式导入Cesium和<a href="https://resium.darwineducation.com/">Resium</a>。<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; <span class="title class_">Color</span> &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;cesium&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; <span class="title class_">Viewer</span>, <span class="title class_">Entity</span> &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;resium&quot;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
